(This structure separates preprocessing from the estimator and guarantees that) Tj
T*
(transformations applied during training are reproduced exactly during evaluation. It also) Tj
T*
(avoids leakage because imputers and encoders are fitted only on the training folds inside) Tj
T*
(the pipeline.) Tj
