T*
() Tj
T*
(- an 80/20 hold-out split,) Tj
T*
(- 5-fold cross-validation,) Tj
T*
(- metrics: R˛, RMSE, and MAE.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The output metrics.json stores both hold-out and cross-validation summaries, along with) Tj
T*
(dataset size and the feature lists used. As a result, the reported numbers are not detached) Tj
T*
(from their methodological context.) Tj
